ohha.puzzlecrafter.auxiliary

Class SingleTimeEntryQueue<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohha.puzzlecrafter.auxiliary.SingleTimeEntryQueue<T>

  • public class SingleTimeEntryQueue<T>
extends Object
    Represents a queue into which elements may be entered only once, regardless of whether they've already exited the queue or not. Made for use in floodfill algorithms, see Fillomino.
